Tipshan, formally known as Marvis Amadi Iguodayela is a Nigerian recording artist, singer, and song writer and performing act. The Edo born artist broke into the industry in the year 2017 with a debut single titled, “GIVE YOU LINE”.   The talented singer is been advertise in the Nigeria music industry as one of the most prominent fast rising stars in the business. Already making a name for him and not only on the street but amongst some of the celebrities.  Tipshan style can best be described as a fusion of both afro sound and reggae vibesand the result is a unique blend that separates the fast rising star from the rest. Since his announcement into the official music platform in 2017, Tipshan has released some well renowned hits like Boat, Manya, his debut single, “give you line”. Over the years, the pop star have gathered a lot fan base and social media following with thousands of listens across all available music.